**Material Information Summary:**

- **Substantial Holder Notice**: Microequities Asset Management Pty Ltd acquired a **7.18% stake** (11,500,000 ordinary shares) in **Stepchange Holdings Limited (STH)**.  
- **Consideration**: **$2.3 million** paid on **2 July 2025**.  
- **Custodian**: JP Morgan Chase Bank holds the shares on behalf of Microequities.  

No further material details identified.
